      "text": "** We can treat them as a \n   value and store them inside \n   a variable.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "** We can treat them as a \n   value and store them inside \n   a variable.",
